- In php there is a server software, we connect script with that but in node.js we create server using javascript code
- In server.js first imp http module, app.js file, and create server using app
- Express app is in app.js handle all routes using 'use' middleware and export file 
- Create a api/routes folder a route container folder
- Create products and order routes with respective http requests and import into app.js
- Show logs in console using morgan module by morgan('dev')
- Error handling message